  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This prospective interventional randomized controlled trial is conducted to compare a new
      technique for Sacrospinous-Sacrotuberous fixation with the traditional sacrospinous ligament
      fixation technique for treatment of uterovaginal and vaginal vault prolapse.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
